Usage: reset_ideal_latency [-help] <object_list> [-fall] [-max] [-min] [-rise]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>          # List of objects: instance pins or ports
                       # (string, required)
-fall                  # Resets ideal latency with respect to fall edge
                       # (bool, optional)
-max                   # Resets ideal latency with respect to max corner
                       # (bool, optional)
-min                   # Resets ideal latency with respect to min corner
                       # (bool, optional)
-rise                  # Resets ideal latency with respect to rise edge
                       # (bool, optional)